HEADWORD: Mantoux test
<hw>Mantoux test</hw> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>A skin
test for hypersensitivity to tuberculin. It determines whether there is
or has been any infection with tubercle bacilli.</def>⟦br⟧
